title: Sawaru no Kinshi!! Ore no Mono.
sinopse:
Akagi Ayane, has been suffering from hyper-responsiveness. This condition is a highly kept secret of hers but everything changes when one of her classmates, Aizawa, discovers it.

Included one-shots:
Kawaii Otoko no Ko no Kaikata
16-sai nanode Kekkon shimasu!!
Anata wa Ouji-sama desu ka!?
